CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Kaspi.kz JSC operates a two-sided Super App business model: the Kaspi.kz Super App for consumers and the Kaspi Pay Super App for merchants and entrepreneurs. With its Super Apps users can access Kaspi.kz's payments, marketplace and fintech solutions which facilitate day-to-day transactions between consumers and merchants. The Kaspi.kz Super App is Kazakhstan's most recognized mobile app.
